it can be divided into the following subsections : pilate 's court ( 27:1 - 2,11-26 ) the death of judas ( 27:3 - 10 ) the soldiers mock jesus ( 27:27 - 31 ) simon of cyrene carries the cross ( 27:32 ) crucifixion of jesus ( 27:33–56 ) joseph of arimathea entombs jesus ( 27:57–61 ) guarding the tomb ( 27:62–66 )   overview matthew describes the trial , crucifixion and burial of jesus .

